desc.value:
鸭子采用老卤水微火慢炖，四川卤味特殊的香味总让大家难以忘怀，我们家卤水别具特色，内含十几种香料国内空运而来，具有色泽棕红、肉质细嫩、香气宜人的特点。鸭子先腌制一晚上，再微火慢卤一小时，于皮，或脆甜，或肥厚，附以细嫩的里肉，口感不输北京烤鸭。
此菜品不辣，喜欢吃辣的朋友请备注加辣椒粉。
desc.pinyin: yā zǐ cǎi yòng lǎo lǔ shǔi wēi huǒ màn tún sì chuān lǔ wèi tè shū de xiāng wèi zǒng ràng dà jiā nán yǐ wàng huái wǒ men jiā lǔ shǔi bié jù tè sè nèi hán shí jī zhǒng xiāng liào guó nèi kōng yùn ér lái jù yǒu sè zé zōng hóng 、 ròu zhí xì nèn 、 xiāng qì yí rén de tè diǎn 。 yā zǐ xiān yān zhì yī wǎn shàng zài wēi huǒ màn lǔ yī xiǎo shí yú pí huò cùi tián huò féi hòu fù yǐ xì nèn de lǐ ròu kǒu gǎn bù shū běi jīng kǎo yā 。 cǐ cài pǐn bù là xǐ huān chī là de péng yǒu qǐng bèi zhù jiā là jiāo fěn 。
desc.translation: Ducks are slowly simmered in old brine. The special scent of Sichuan brine is always unforgettable. Our family's brine is unique. It contains more than a dozen spices from China. It has the characteristics of brown and red color, delicate meat and pleasant aroma . Ducks are marinated overnight, then simmered slowly for an hour. The skin is either crispy or thick, and it is tender and tender. It tastes like a Beijing roast duck. This dish is not spicy. If you like spicy food, please add chili powder.
